The enlarger, along with various items of printing equipment, was donated to the museum by Mariaan Lombard. A fully-equipped darkroom has already been set up at the museum.
It is planned to open the museum in 2021. Newspapers and individuals who wish to make donations to the museum are asked to please phone Tobie van den Bergh, director for the Forum for Community Journalists at 072 2220 1568, or e-mail him atÂ tobie@mobserver.co.za. The history of community newspapers will be displayed on blocked boards, and space has also been provided on which to display old photographs.